<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password - Grocey</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(7, 138, 7, 0.05), rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.03)); padding: 40px 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(7, 138, 7, 0.15); overflow: hidden; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(7, 138, 7), rgb(76, 175, 80)); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .logo-section { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .logo { width: 48px; height: 48px; margin-right: 16px; }
        .brand-name { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; }
        .title-msg { font-size: 24px; margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-weight: 400; opacity: 0.95; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; }
        .shield-icon { width: 28px; height: 28px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .reset-section { background: rgb(248, 250, 252); border: 2px solid rgb(7, 138, 7); border-radius: 12px; padding: 30px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .reset-label { font-size: 18px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: 500; }
        .code-container { position: relative; display: inline-block; }
        .reset-code { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(7, 138, 7); letter-spacing: 4px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; background: white; padding: 15px 25px; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid rgb(7, 138, 7); margin: 10px; }
        .copy-btn { position: absolute; top: 50%; right: -45px; transform: translateY(-50%); background: rgb(7, 138, 7); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 6px; width: 36px; height: 36px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.2s ease; }
        .copy-btn:hover { background: rgb(5, 100, 5); transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.05); }
        .copy-icon { width: 16px; height: 16px; }
        .instructions { color: #666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 25px 0; }
        .security-tips { background: rgba(7, 138, 7, 0.05); border-left: 4px solid rgb(7, 138, 7); padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; }
        .security-title { color: rgb(7, 138, 7); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 16px; }
        .security-list { color: #666; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; }
        .security-list li { margin: 5px 0; }
        .footer { background: rgb(248, 250, 252); padding: 25px 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
        .footer-text { color: #888; font-size: 14px; }
        .highlight { color: rgb(7, 138, 7); font-weight: 600; }
        @media (max-width: 600px) { .container { margin: 0 10px; } .header { padding: 30px 20px; } .content { padding: 30px 20px; } .brand-name { font-size: 28px; } .title-msg { font-size: 20px; } .reset-code { font-size: 28px; padding: 12px 20px; } .copy-btn { right: -40px; width: 32px; height: 32px; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-section">
                <svg class="logo" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M17,18C17.56,18 18,18.44 18,19C18,19.56 17.56,20 17,20C16.44,20 16,19.56 16,19C16,18.44 16.44,18 17,18M1,2V4H3L6.6,11.59L5.24,14.04C5.09,14.32 5,14.65 5,15A2,2 0 0,0 7,17H19V15H7.42A0.25,0.25 0 0,1 7.17,14.75C7.17,14.7 7.18,14.66 7.2,14.63L8.1,13H15.55C16.3,13 16.96,12.58 17.3,11.97L20.88,5H5.21L4.27,3H1M7,18C7.56,18 8,18.44 8,19C8,19.56 7.56,20 7,20C6.44,20 6,19.56 6,19C6,18.44 6.44,18 7,18Z" />
                </svg>
                <h1 class="brand-name">Grocey</h1>
            </div>
            <h2 class="title-msg">
                <svg class="shield-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M12,1L3,5V11C3,16.55 6.84,21.74 12,23C17.16,21.74 21,16.55 21,11V5L12,1M12,7C13.4,7 14.8,8.6 14.8,10V11.5C15.4,11.5 16,12.4 16,13V16C16,17.4 15.4,18 14.8,18H9.2C8.6,18 8,17.4 8,16V13C8,12.4 8.6,11.5 9.2,11.5V10C9.2,8.6 10.6,7 12,7M12,8.2C11.2,8.2 10.5,8.7 10.5,10V11.5H13.5V10C13.5,8.7 12.8,8.2 12,8.2Z" />
                </svg>
                Password Recovery
            </h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            
            
            <div class="reset-section">
                <div class="reset-label">Your password reset code is:</div>
                <div class="code-container">
                    <div class="reset-code" id="resetCode"><%VERIFICATION_CODE%></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="instructions">
                <p><strong>We received a request to reset your Grocey password.</strong></p>
                <p>Enter this code in the app to create a new password. If you didn't request this, please <span class="danger">ignore this email</span> and your password will remain unchanged.</p>
            </div>
            
            
        </div>
        
        
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>
